<h1> Hello, Welcome to Xin Zhao's DevOps Demo Project !!   </h1>

<h2> Any modification in Git Repo (https://github.com/xinzhao219/hello-world.git) will invoke the pipeline. </h2>
<h2> This DevOps CI/CD Pipeline includes four steps: </h2>

<h3> 1. Pull the latest Ansible and Kubernetes scripts from Github (https://github.com/xinzhao219/DevOpsDemo.git) </h3>
<h3>2. Build and make a docker image for the demo project with Maven, Docker </h3>
<h3>3. Push the new image to the DockerHub. </h3>
<h3>4. Call the CD-Pipeline to deploy the image to the Kubernetes cluster. </h3>




